summary: A goal-driven health care professional with national and international experience in clinical rehabilitation, quantitative and qualitative scientific research on communicable and noncommunicable diseases. Enthusiastic and highly motivated to accomplish goals efficiently and acquire new skills that are key for new insights into the health care industry. Particular interest in public health projects and innovative medicine market to provide high standard health care advice that benefits the community and the healthcare system globally.
